flowchart TD
  UI[Reader / Socratic Page]
  UI -->|Ask question| AppCmd[Wails Backend Command]
  AppCmd -->|"ProcessQuery(topicID, question)"| RAG[RAG Pipeline]

  subgraph RAGPipeline[RAG Pipeline]
    V[Validate topic exists]
    C[Fetch topic content & chunks]
    S[Search top-k relevant chunks]
    H[Apply heuristic scoring]
    E[Expand to parent sections]
    P[Assemble prompt within token budget]
    L[Call LLM provider]
    R[Build response + citations]
  end

  AppCmd --> RAG
  RAG --> V
  V --> C
  C --> S
  S --> H
  H --> E
  E --> P
  P --> L
  L --> R
  R -->|Answer + cited_sections| AppCmd
  AppCmd -->|return| UI

  subgraph Data[Local Data]
    DB[SQLite DB]
    Vec[sqlite-vec vector index]
    Assets[Tokenizer + ONNX model]
  end

  C -->|topic metadata| DB
  C -->|chunk metadata| DB
  S -->|embedding search| Vec
  P -->|token counts| Assets
  L -->|embeddings| Assets
  L -->|HTTP request| Provider[OpenAI-compatible LLM API]

  style RAGPipeline fill:#eef6ff,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:1px
  style Data fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:1px
  style UI fill:#f8fafb,stroke:#60a5fa,stroke-width:1px
